                                <div class="intro-container">
                                    <h1>Port Forwarding</h1>
                                    <h3>Setting up port forwarding in your Telekom Speedport</h3>
                                    <p class="intro">
                                      To access your camera through the internet you will need a portforwarding service inside your router. For more general information about the ddns access please refer to <a href="http://wiki.instar.com/index.php/The_DDNS_Service">HERE</a>.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
